          "unwalked": [],
          "npcs": [
            {
              "name": "Man o' war",
              "description": "Hrmm, you can't guarantee a stab at its back would hit anything vital. Most of the furniture here is rotten and falling apart, but it seems that this was once a hall used to entertain guests.  Some tattered trappings hang on the wall, depicting battles so old you can't recall ever hearing of them.  A large window looks like it'll take you back outside the tower. An immense, wooden banquet table lies in ruins. A blobby mess schlumps about the area. A large black fiddler crab menacingly waves its one massive claw. A blobby mess schlumps about the area. A strange looking frog hops about. Years of neglect ha weathered this once magnificeintly ornate banquet table.  Such a pity as you can almost hear the ghost of long-past revelers table. A broken banquet table is a select item, too heavy to lift and much larger than you are.",
              "unique": false,
              "npc_type": "trash"
            }
          ],
